                "paragraphOrdinal": 6,
                "paragraphTitle": null,
                "paragraphSubtitles": [
                  "Something's happening at the bank. It's on the radio. The police are looking for a man with a gray coat and a bag with a lot of money."
                ],
                "paragraphContents": [
                  "I have a bag, but it doesn't have any money in it! It's your bag … from the restaurant last night."
